</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uinfinitestorms.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Infinite Storms</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/13/01 10:07:17 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Verant can kiss my A$$</span><hr size=1> Nm. Im not wasting my time anymore. Nice. Wizard is the only class for me. I dont have any alt's/twinks, but I bet you do eh?  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uinfinitestorms.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Infinite Storms</A> at: 5/13/01 10:15:37 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uwraithwavefeaamael.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Wraithwave FeaAmael</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://keith.vaughan.home.mindspring.com/img/ball3.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/13/01 11:27:59 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Yes sir...</span><hr size=1> We have all had our moments with the group problem.  Except those who don't mind soloing until the end of time.  Alts or not, it is a horrible way to live.  I feel the pain as well.<br>
<br>
W.F. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uvabannloosecannon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vabann Loosecannon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/13/01 11:54:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Yes sir...</span><hr size=1> Damn straight I have alts/twinks.  Wizards sux0r!<br>
