<br>
Plenty of content there you probably missed the first time around, or new content that has been added.  FUN content.  <br>
<br>
It's a game, get what you want out of it.  You don't have fun, cancel.<br>
<br>
Wizards can't raid.  Tanks can't solo.<br>
Wizards can't double backstab.  Rogues can't AoE.<br>
<br>
Seriously, play another class.  You'll miss your wizard.<br>
<br>
[WARNING: not so humble and unpopular opinion coming...]<br>
<br>
I happen to like playing taxi for my guild tanks.  I'm there to socialize/travel/see new content.<br>
<br>
And, I honestly don't see why everyone thinks wizards should do as much damage over time as a melee.  Makes no sense to me at all.  I don't think wizards are that 'broken'.  We do need to be more group friendly, which was the point of this thread, and sounds like Verant *may* be doing something about that (about friggin' time).<br>
<br>
[End: not so humble opinion and unpopular opinion]<br>
<br>
Play another class or cancel. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
